Anne Nagel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anne_Nagel 0 Anne Nagel (September 29, 1915 – July 6, 1966) was an American actress. She played in adventures, mysteries, and comedies for twenty-five years. She also appeared in television series in the 1950s. One book described her as "one of Hollywood's true hard-luck gals." Anne_Nagel ( September_29_,_1915 – July_6_,_1966 ) was an_American_actress .
